# Clive Worker
#
# NOTE: All environment variables are loaded from the MONOREPO ROOT .env file.
# See /.env.example for the complete list of configuration options.
#
# Do NOT create a .env file in this directory.
# Instead, add your variables to the root /.env file.
#
# Required variables for worker:
#   CLIVE_WORKER_TOKEN     - API token (must match CLIVE_WORKER_API_TOKEN on central service)
#   CLIVE_CENTRAL_URL      - WebSocket URL of central service (wss://...)
#
# Project configuration (choose one):
#   CLIVE_WORKSPACE_ROOT   - Single project path
#   CLIVE_WORKSPACE_ROOTS  - Comma-separated project paths
#   CLIVE_PROJECTS         - JSON array with full project metadata
#   CLIVE_PROJECTS_FILE    - Path to JSON config file
